items.title: Centre imposes non-tariff barrier to curb imports of solar cells, boost local production
items.description: The Ministry of New and Renewable Energy has stated that solar cells will be included in the approved list of models and manufacturers (ALMM) from June 1, 2026

items.title: Business News Live: Asian stocks rally on optimism over China stimulus
items.description: Business News Live: Benchmark stock indexes in China and Hong Kong both jumped from the open, while those in Japan and South Korea also climbed

items.title: Just Climate, Morgan Stanley Infra Partners-backed Continuum Green Energy files for Rs 3,650-crore IPO
items.description: Founded by Arvind Bansal and Vikash Saraf in 2009, Continuum Green Energy focuses on supplying green power to commercial & industrial consumers
